tags.name: MacArthur Boulevard
tags.note: Speed limit is 35 MPH from SH-180 to just north of I-30. North of I-30 and into Irving, it becomes 40. After Hunter Farrell Road, it increases to 45. Before Oakdale Road, its reduced to 35.
